WEBVTT

00:00:28.519 --> 00:00:30.420
Bu imildoq bo'lib,

00:00:30.420 --> 00:00:33.289
sakkiz oyoqli marmeladli 
ayiqqa o'xshasa-da,

00:00:33.289 --> 00:00:38.049
u yer yuzidagi eng kuchli 
mavjudotlardan biri hisoblanadi.

00:00:38.049 --> 00:00:40.749
Aksariyat organizmlarning 
hayoti suvga bog'liq.

00:00:40.749 --> 00:00:43.059
Suv hujayralardagi barcha

00:00:43.059 --> 00:00:46.080
biokimyoviy reaksiyalarni 
yo'lga qo'yuvchi

00:00:46.080 --> 00:00:49.249
metabolizm jarayoni uchun juda muhim.

00:00:49.249 --> 00:00:53.409
Biroq "suv ayig'i" laqabini olgan 
imildoq kabi mavjudotlar

00:00:53.409 --> 00:00:58.069
bu cheklovni angidrobioz 
(yunoncha "suvsiz hayot")

00:00:58.069 --> 00:01:01.100
orqali yengib o'tadilar.
Qanchalar g'ayrioddiy tuyulmasin,